        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8228",
        "content": "Nevertheless, there was no law against a man's belief; therefore, a man was punished only for the crimes which he had done; therefore all men were on equal grounds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
